  "materials_text": "",
  "steps": [
    "Quantitative Real-Time RT-PCR Assay Applying Calibrated mRNA Reference (Ctrl Mix)",
    "I.Reverse transcription reaction",
    "1. For each set of labeling reaction, add the following and mix gently:",
    "1)Purified total RNA (2 µg)¬_ µl",
    "2)Oligo (dT)18 (0.5 µg/µl) 1 µl",
    "3)dNTP Mix (10mM)1 µl",
    "4)Ctrl Mix 1 µl",
    "5)H2O¬¬_ µl",
    "____________",
    "Total13 µl",
    "2.Mix well and incubate at 65°C for 5 min",
    "3.Chill on ice for at least 1 min",
    "4.Add the following and mix gently:",
    "1)5x First Strand Buffer4 µl",
    "2)0.1 M DTT1 µl",
    "3)SuperScript III (200 U/µl)1 µl",
    "4)RNaseOUT (40 U/µl) 1 µl",
    "__________",
    "Total7 µl",
    "Final reaction volume = 20 µl",
    "5.Incubate at 50°C for 1 hr, 70°C for 15 min, and 4°C to end the reaction using a PCR cycler",
    "II. PCR Reaction",
    "6. For each reaction, add the following and mix well gently:",
    "1)2x SybrGreen MasterMix ¬12.5 µl",
    "2)Forward Primer (10 mM) 0.5 µl",
    "3)Reverse Primer (10 mM) 0.5 µl",
    "4)Template 0.25 µl",
    "5)H2O¬¬ 11.25 µl",
    "_______________",
    "Total 25 µl",
    "7. Run reactions with the following thermal profile:",
    "Stage 1: 95°C for 3 min",
    "Stage 2: 40 cycles of",
    "[Step 1: 95°C for 15 sec and",
    "Step 2: 60°C for 45 sec]",
    "Stage 3: Step 1: 95°C for 15 sec",
    "Step 2: 60°C for 1 min and",
    "Step 3: 95°C for 15 sec",
    "Stage 4:Run dissociation curve",
    "(Step 1: 95°C for 15 sec",
    "Step 2: 60°C for 1 min and",
    "Step 3: 95°C for 15 sec)",
    "Settings:",
    "Sample volume: 25 µl",
    "Stat Collection: stage 2 step 2 (60°C @0.45)",
    "Note: Run a separate dissociation program after completion of the PCR reaction in case it is not included in the instrument profile settings. This is to confirm the reaction is gene specific and free from the primer dimmer effects."
